## Execution Architecture (System 1)
Seven rules enforced before every trade:
1. Position awareness -- no duplicate positions in same asset same direction
2. Market hours routing -- equities and leveraged ETFs only 9:30-4:00 ET weekdays
3. Allocation limits -- equity 40%, crypto 20%, leveraged ETF 30%, single position 15%
4. Direction conflict -- close existing position before reversing
5. Daily loss limit -- 3% drawdown halts all trading for the day
6. VIX circuit breaker -- reduce size 50% above 35, stop equity trading above 50
7. Duplicate signal prevention -- same signal blocked for 2 cycles after execution

## Execution Architecture (System 2)
